item.title: Hash Code 2020
item.description: Hello Everyone, I want to share our solution for Google Hash Code 2020. It is the code repo of team titanium-white for Google Hash Code 2020 Online Qualification Round. We have writen our code in Python. Code can be reached from here Code Basically, the problem class is the backbone of the system. It handles the inputs and outputs with functions __init__ and dump. It read the input files and creates objects according to that.
